snippet.title: Survive10MinutesPlease Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay of the game "Survive10MinutesPlease".

About Game:
Survive10MinutesPlease is an action Roguelike game where you have to survive 10 minutes against several enemies using different weapons and tactics.
